##### LAPTOP(1).csv
**#### Title: Laptop Dataset**

**Description**: This dataset contains information about various laptops, including their name, price, star rating, customer reviews, processor details, storage capacity, operating system, RAM, and display specifications.

**Columns**:

name: Name of the laptop
price: Price of the laptop
star: Star rating of the laptop
Rating_and_Review: Combined field for rating and review
processor: Processor details
capacity: Storage capacity
os: Operating system
ram: RAM size
Display: Display details


**##### Laptop_cleaning_datasets**
**## Title: Cleaned Laptop Dataset
**
**Description**: This dataset is a cleaned version of the original laptop dataset, with additional columns for processor brand, processor type, processor generation, RAM type, operating system name, operating system version, operating system architecture, and display size in both centimeters and inches.

**Columns:**

name: Name of the laptop
Brand: Brand of the laptop
price: Price of the laptop
star: Star rating of the laptop
Rating_and_Review: Combined field for rating and review
Rating: Rating of the laptop
Review: Customer review of the laptop
processor: Processor details
Processor_Brand: Brand of the processor
Processor_Type: Type of the processor
Processor_Generation: Generation of the processor
capacity: Storage capacity
RAM_Size: Size of RAM
RAM_Type: Type of RAM
os: Operating system
Operating_System_Name: Name of the operating system
Operating_System_Version: Version of the operating system
Operating System Architecture: Architecture of the operating system
ram: RAM size
Storage Capacity: Storage capacity
Storage Type: Type of storage
Storage Unit: Unit of storage
Display: Display details
Display Size (cm): Display size in centimeters
Display Size (inch): Display size in inches
